":"ذا","tier":"q100","transliteration":"dhālika"},{"id":"ac-79:26:6","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":26,"wordNum":6,"arabic":"خَشِيَ","targetTranslation":"he fears/is fearing","ayahArabic":"إِنَّ فِى ذٰلِكَ لَعِبْرَةً لِّمَن يَخْشَىٰٓ","ayahEnglish":"Indeed in that is a lesson [i.e., warning] for whoever would fear [Allāh].","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["he loved","he hoped","he denied"],"pos":"V","lemma":"خَشِيَ","tier":"q300","transliteration":"yakhshā"},{"id":"ac-79:27:1","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":27,"wordNum":1,"arabic":"أ","targetTranslation":"are you all?","ayahArabic":"ءَأَنتُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ بَنَىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"Are you a more difficult creation or is the heaven? He [i.e., Allāh] constructed it.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["command","fire","book"],"pos":"N","lemma":"أ","tier":"q100","transliteration":"a-antum"},{"id":"ac-79:27:2","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":27,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"أَشَدّ","targetTranslation":"stronger/more intense (than خَلْقًا)","ayahArabic":"ءَأَنتُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ بَنَىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"Are you a more difficult creation or is the heaven? He [i.e., Allāh] constructed it.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["sweeter","nearer","clearer"],"pos":"N","lemma":"أَشَدّ","tier":"q600","transliteration":"ashaddu"},{"id":"ac-79:27:3","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":27,"wordNum":3,"arabic":"خَلْق","targetTranslation":"a creation (object of أَشَدُّ/stronger)","ayahArabic":"ءَأَنتُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ بَنَىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"Are you a more difficult creation or is the heaven? He [i.e., Allāh] constructed it.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["Judgment","Guidance","Punishment"],"pos":"N","lemma":"خَلْق","tier":"q300","transliteration":"khalqan"},{"id":"ac-79:27:6","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":27,"wordNum":6,"arabic":"بَنَى","targetTranslation":"he built it (referring to Allah building the sky)","ayahArabic":"ءَأَنتُمْ أَشَدُّ خَلْقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ بَنَىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"Are you a more difficult creation or is the heaven? He [i.e., Allāh] constructed it.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["constructed","established","erected"],"pos":"V","lemma":"بَنَى","tier":"q1000","transliteration":"banāhā"},{"id":"ac-79:28:1","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":28,"wordNum":1,"arabic":"رَفَعَ","targetTranslation":"he raised (subject of فَسَوَّىٰهَا)","ayahArabic":"رَفَعَ سَمْكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"He raised its ceiling and proportioned it.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["he lifted","he elevated","he promoted"],"pos":"V","lemma":"رَفَعَ","tier":"q600","transliteration":"rafaʿa"},{"id":"ac-79:28:2","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":28,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"سَمْك","targetTranslation":"its height (object of رَفَعَ/He raised)","ayahArabic":"رَفَعَ سَمْكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"He raised its ceiling and proportioned it.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["its people","(the) slightest sound of it","its provision"],"pos":"N","lemma":"سَمْك","tier":"q_all","transliteration":"samkahā"},{"id":"ac-79:29:2","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":29,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"لَيْل","targetTranslation":"its night (object of أَغْطَشَ - He darkened)","ayahArabic":"وَأَغْطَشَ لَيْلَهَا وَأَخْرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"And He darkened its night and extracted its brightness.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["sea","balance","sign"],"pos":"N","lemma":"لَيْل","tier":"q300","transliteration":"laylahā"},{"id":"ac-79:29:4","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":29,"wordNum":4,"arabic":"ضُحًى","targetTranslation":"its morning brightness (object of أَخْرَجَ - He brought forth)","ayahArabic":"وَأَغْطَشَ لَيْلَهَا وَأَخْرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","ayahEnglish":"And He darkened its night and extracted its brightness.","blankPosition":-1,"distractors":["forever","night","ten"],"pos":"N","lemma":"ضُحًى","tier":"q_all","transliteration":"ḍuḥāhā"},{"id":"ac-79:30:2","surahNum":79,"ayahNum":30,"wordNum":2,"arabic":"بَعْد","targetTranslation":"after (connects to دَحَىٰهَآ - He spread it)","ayahArabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ بَعْدَ ذٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","ayahE